Maggs on Media with Jeremy Maggs Maggs on Media is a powerful digest of media issues and topical advertising. This weekly programme features the good, the bad - and the newsworthy of the media world. Presenter Jeremy Maggs' extensive experience in the media industry makes him an informed facilitator of discussions on issues facing the media. Regular insights from leading local and global thinkers mean viewers are exposed to trends affecting brand communications and the new technologies driving them. An active social media community also share their thoughts on programme content and often influence what is covered on the show. Phone: 011 537 9300 Twitter: @Maggsonmedia Facebook: Maggs on media  